<!-- ABSTRACT -->
<h2>Abstract</h2>
<p>In the modern digital landscape, creating a comprehensive marketing campaign across multiple platforms requires extensive time, copywriting expertise, and systemized data analytics. To solve this, the <strong>Marketing Campaign Generator</strong> is proposed as an all-in-one, AI-driven automation platform.</p>
<p>Built leveraging cutting-edge web technologies such as Next.js, React, and TypeScript alongside powerful Generative AI tools (Google Gemini and OpenAI), this platform translates simple human-readable project briefs into full-scale, multi-channel marketing campaigns. In a matter of minutes, the system autonomously drafts platform-specific headlines, ad copies, targeted email sequences, and analytical schemas natively via prompt ingestion.</p>
<p>The application features a highly responsive frontend, utilizing advanced mathematics to render moving particles and 3D mockups via Framer Motion. Secure authentication is handled through NextAuth.js combined with Drizzle ORM pushing to an internal SQLite engine, ensuring maximal data protection through BcryptJS hashing mechanisms.</p>

